name: Finnair A350 Business Class Flight Review
description:
Get a free 30 day trial for Audible at http://audible.com/dennisbunnik or text
‘dennisbunnik’ to 500-500

It's time to fly!  This time I'm on the beautiful Finnair A350 in business class from Tokyo Narita to Helsinki, Finland. 

This Finnair Business Class flight review covers the JAL Sakura Lounge at Narita, boarding, take off, the wonderful Finnair inflight service and business class seat. 

For more flight reviews please check out my channel or the links at the bottom of this description.  

Route:    Tokyo Narita (NRT) to Helsinki (HEL)
Length:  4,870 miles,  10 hrs
Flight:     AY74
When:    March 2018
Aircraft:  Airbus A350-9   registration OH-LWB - Oct 2015 (One World Livery)
Seat:       11L
Camera:  Sony FDR-AXP55
